msgid "The silhouette of a large clock is reflected here."
msgstr "這裡映照著一座大鐘的輪廓。"

msgid "A large window shaped like a clock towers above you."
msgstr "一扇形狀像鐘的大窗戶聳立在你的上方。"

msgid "The time is set to 12:00."
msgstr "時間設定在 12:00。"

msgid "There you are!"
msgstr "妳在這啊！"

msgid "How'd you get in there?"
msgstr "妳怎麼進去的？"

msgid "I got zapped, like there's something keeping me out."
msgstr "我被擊退，就像是有東西在阻止我進去。"

msgid "Really?"
msgstr "真的嗎？"

msgid "You didn't even notice me gone!?"
msgstr "妳根本沒注意到我不見了！？"

msgid "...."
msgstr "...."

msgid "No."
msgstr "沒有。"

msgid "Cold..."
msgstr "真冷酷..."

msgid "So what was in there anyway?"
msgstr "所以裡面有什麼？"

msgid "Anything fun?"
msgstr "有什麼好玩的嗎？"

msgid "Yes, very fun."
msgstr "是啊，很好玩。"

msgid "What? Really??"
msgstr "什麼？真的嗎？？"

msgid "What was it?"
msgstr "是什麼？"

msgid "I can't tell you."
msgstr "我不能告訴你。"

msgid "Huh?!"
msgstr "蛤？！"

msgid "Why not??"
msgstr "為什麼不能？？"

msgid "Because it's more fun that way."
msgstr "因為這樣比較好玩。"

msgid "No way, don't do me dirty like this!"
msgstr "怎麼可能，不要這樣對我！"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "(It's strange though. Why wasn't he able to enter?)"
msgstr "(真是奇怪。為什麼他沒辦法進去？)"
